mbinenarrowly missed out on a medal in the final of the men's100mat theParis Olympicson Sunday evening.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.4477892334995956e-12, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simbine clocked9.82- a new South African record - but finished fourth.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AmericanNoah Lylestook the gold medal in a personal best of 9.79, ahead of Jamaica'sKishane Thompson(9.79), withFred Kerley(United States) in third (9.81).\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 730, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999856121751743, \"rank\": 1.4352468203625066e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9663561948267746, \"rank\": 0.0348151178236916, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"