mericanKenny Bednarekwith his compatriotFred Kerleyin Lane 2.Kishane Thompsonof Jamaica will start in Lane 3 with Simbine in the next lane followed by Jamaica'sOblique Sevillein Lane 5.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999856121751743, \"rank\": 1.4352468203625066e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lanes 6-8 will be filled by AmericanNoah Lyles,Letsile Tebogoof Botswana and defending 100m Olympic champion,Lamont Jacobsof Italy, respectively.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9999063592466743, \"rank\": 8.439551715582567e-05, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999950041456, \"rank\": 4.3523571883514205e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanford_and_Son\", \"score\": 0.9999999999713509, \"rank\": 2.8625061708167512e-11, \"text\": \"Lamont\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanford_and_Son\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanford_and_Son\"}, {\"begin\": 1436, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6921483613272529, \"rank\": 0.4151447631858418, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org